(3, 1, '191', 'Crystal Structure', 1, 1, 'At the end of the lesson students should be able to Define Crystal structure, Describe the various crystal lattice, distinguish between crystalline solids and amorphous solids', 'In this lesson we get to look at the types of solids Crystalline and non crystalline subject. Its expected you review Atom, ions and molecules as well as the structure of matter. ', 5, '2020-08-23 17:24:00', '2020-12-25 19:24:00', 0, 0, '2020-08-25 16:30:00'),
