(6, 7, '190', 'Lesson 2', 1, 1, 'The objective of this weeks\' lesson is to recall some Primary 5 class topics and content we should be able to resolve problems related to these topics at the end of the class. Do have a great learning experience.', 'Welcome to week 2 of our learning series for incoming students into JSS1. For other classes you may find the quantitative and verbal reasoning useful as you prepare for the JIC entrance test.', 5, '2020-09-14 05:17:00', '2020-11-03 05:18:00', 0, 0, '2020-09-03 04:18:11'),
